      "featured-image": {
        "fileId": "677deb561a16b5faec45660f",
        "url": "https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6764ce480fea74a61cc3a6d3/677deb561a16b5faec45660f_JLL_Melbourne_HighRes-6-1140x760.jpg",
        "alt": null
      },
      "summary": "Connecting heritage-inspired design with modern functionality, we're proud to deliver flooring that provides the foundation for a space balancing history, innovation, and sustainability.",
      "project-managers": [
        "6771d4fc86aa61c0b57d2dbb"
      ],
      "description": "<p id=\"\">JLL\u2019s new Melbourne headquarters at the prestigious 101 Collins Street blends Melbourne\u2019s history with bold, modern design.</p><p id=\"\">Spanning two levels, the space takes inspiration from Melbourne\u2019s heritage in Flinders Lane, crafting a workspace that balances historical character with contemporary function and sustainability.</p><p id=\"\">Premrest was proud to play a key role in this project, installing the floors that provide the foundation for this dynamic office. The design called for finishes that could seamlessly link the polished charm of Collins Street with the gritty, industrious vibe of Flinders Lane, and we delivered flooring solutions that meet this brief while standing up to the demands of a busy commercial space.</p><p id=\"\">By blending warm and refined finishes with more industrial textures, the floors reflect the contrast between the city\u2019s past and its forward-thinking present.</p><p id=\"\">The flooring plays a central role in client-facing spaces like the new \u2018Business Lounge,\u2019 a first for JLL. This area needed to feel welcoming and professional, and our flooring solutions helped create a space that elevates client interactions and leaves a lasting impression. For the team spaces, we focused on durability and comfort, ensuring the floors support productivity while still looking great.</p><p id=\"\">At Premrest, we\u2019re all about making spaces work \u2014 and work well. For JLL\u2019s headquarters, that meant installing flooring that could handle heavy foot traffic, align perfectly with the design vision, and provide long-lasting quality. From start to finish, we made it happen with a practical, no-fuss approach that delivered exceptional results.</p>"
